Gruebel Lost UBS Board’s Confidence Before Resignation, SZ Says

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-09-25T07:22:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/gruebel-lost-ubs-board-s-confidence-before-resignation-sz-says.html
Oswald Gruebel  lost the unanimous
support of the  UBS AG (UBSN)  board before before resigning yesterday as
the bank’s chief executive officer,  SonntagsZeitung  reported.  Gruebel was opposed to an early resignation, the Zurich-
based newspaper said, citing unidentified people close to the
situation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Geneva at 
 gbroom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly in Paris at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  